The last step included the analysis of the experiments by using the analysis of variance F statistic (ANOVA F Statistic). Such a method compares the variability between the groups to the variability within the groups. The formula used for the ANOVA F Statistic for each node of the network-based model is:3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
